OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784908087
OL,3,CThieves smash into cafe during
OL,4,Cburglary leaving owner #40,000 out of
OL,5,Cpocket
OL,7,FA cafe owner from Banbury in
OL,8,FOxfordshire says he's been left
OL,9,F#40,000 out of pocket following a
OL,10,Fburglary.
OL,12,FFour masked men, armed with crowbars
OL,13,Fbroke into Reg's Cafe on Sunday 5 July.
OL,15,FAs well as stealing stock and
OL,16,Fequipment they also caused extensive
OL,17,Fdamage.
OL,26,@uD@Urr
