FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784908087
OL,3,CThieves smash into cafe during
OL,4,Cburglary leaving owner #40,000 out of
OL,5,Cpocket
OL,7,FOwner Reg Howe has been running the
OL,8,Fbusiness for 14 years and says he's
OL,9,Fdevastated. He received a call from
OL,10,Fthe alarm company, alerting him to the
OL,11,Fbreak-in.
OL,13,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, he said: "My
OL,14,Finitial reaction was obviously to jump
OL,15,Fout of bed, get in my car and get to
OL,16,Four premises whilst at the same time
OL,17,Fcalling the police to tell them it's a
OL,18,Fconfirmed breakin.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784908087
OL,3,CThieves smash into cafe during
OL,4,Cburglary leaving owner #40,000 out of
OL,5,Cpocket
OL,7,F"We were actually watching the
OL,8,Findividuals rob us as we made our way
OL,9,Fto the premises.
OL,11,F"It's soul-destroying because we work
OL,12,Fseven days a week, and to have
OL,13,Fsomebody literally take your
OL,14,Flivelihood, smash up your premises, it
OL,15,Fleaves certainly for my family, along
OL,16,Fwith me, mental scars afterwards.
OL,18,F"Your space has been violated by
OL,19,Fpeople that clearly have no idea about
OL,20,Fworking.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784908087
OL,3,CThieves smash into cafe during
OL,4,Cburglary leaving owner #40,000 out of
OL,5,Cpocket
OL,7,F"They just come and rob what they want
OL,8,Fto do what they want and I just think
OL,9,Fit's shocking in today's age that that
OL,10,Fmentality still exists."
OL,12,FReg has estimated the losses to be in
OL,13,Fthe region of #40,000.
OL,15,FThe building was ransacked and the
OL,16,Ffront window smashed.
OL,18,FThousands of pounds worth of stock and
OL,19,Fequipment was stolen, as well as
OL,20,Fdamage caused with the office broken
OL,21,Finto and cupboard doors ripped off.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784908087
OL,3,CThieves smash into cafe during
OL,4,Cburglary leaving owner #40,000 out of
OL,5,Cpocket
OL,7,FThe thieves even stole smaller items
OL,8,Flike ketchup and cans of fizzy drinks.
OL,10,F"The most valuable bit they did get
OL,11,Fwere some spare keys and building
OL,12,Fkeys," Reg added.
OL,14,F"So we've had to go through the
OL,15,Fprocess immediately of changing all
OL,16,Fthe locks, some car keys have had to
OL,17,Fbe changed which is a very expensive
OL,18,Fjob."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784908087
OL,3,CThieves smash into cafe during
OL,4,Cburglary leaving owner #40,000 out of
OL,5,Cpocket
OL,7,FDetective Inspector Robert Platt,
OL,8,Fbased at Banbury police station, said:
OL,9,F"We are investigating a burglary at
OL,10,FReg's Cafe and Banbury Van & Car Hire
OL,11,Fon Thorpe Way, Banbury, at around 11pm
OL,12,Fon 5 July.
OL,14,F"No arrests have been made so far but
OL,15,Four enquiries are ongoing, including
OL,16,Fliaising with neighbouring forces
OL,17,Fabout similar offences that may be
OL,18,Flinked to the same offenders.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@JrrvD@AOU
